dialogue: Hi Emma! My name is Frosty :penguin: and I’m here to help you learn all about science:microscope:, verbal reasoning (GRE) :input_latin_uppercase:, and safety:hammer_and_wrench:!
I ask you questions, and you give me answers.
We will learn fun things together!
Let's test your knowledge on science!
What kind of viscosity is found in long-chain hydrocarbons?
Which of the following options is the right answer?

:keycap_1: low viscosity
:keycap_2: high viscosity
:keycap_3: increased viscosity
:keycap_4: intense viscosity
